summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-fourth Avenue and Thirty-fourth Avenue North from East Pike Street to a point 204 feet south of East John Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing watermains under Ordinance No. 19019, creating Local Improvement District No. 1827 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
